  "stemHtml": "<p>Refer to figures or CAP 698 files 4.8 and 4.9. <br>Given the following information, find V<strong><sub>1</sub></strong>, V<strong><sub>R</sub></strong> and V<strong><sub>2</sub></strong> speeds for a MRJT aeroplane:</p><p>Airport Elevation: 1000 ft <br>RWY 24 <br>Slope: 1% UP <br>QNH: 1013 hPa <br>OAT: +15\u00b0C <br>W/V: 240\u00b0/35 kt <br>TOM: 60 700 kg <br>Flaps: 5\u00b0</p>",
